column5: Means I may just be able to go Muskie hunting next week if I can get this thing loaded and on it's way back to Montreal on Saturday..
Ok Wayne - I know you want to go muskey hunting - but am I missing something here? - Where are the wings!!!!!?    Don
They don't need them in Kabec!  ....and besides... Santa don' t need no wings!
Looking good!!  Hey, is that some new V-tail I've never seen?
I take it it's there just so you could give the motor a try not there for good...LOL
That's the weirdest snow blower I've ever seen. The front mounted auger looks powerful though.   Hookset.
a few skis  on it and who needs an argo or sled

Well..... time to go see if the boat launch is usable!  Another happy customer on his way. Hope he makes it to Montreal with the weather of today! Left at 12:30, should be 2/3rds there I HOPE!
